{"tid":678417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家傭涉女主人食物中「加尿」被捕","createTime":"2018-05-26T05:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T14:09:41.000Z","uid":34495,"like":109,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e701105dcf42eb74d92731b68883a4b944b3de6b","tid":678417,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180526/s00001/1527311196745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180526%2Fs00001%2F1527311196745&d=j0YDAcivOU%2FYqdyyERvDjxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=5c319fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180526%2Fs00001%2F1527311196745&h=edf77ef7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180526/s00001/1527311196745</a><br />\n<br />\n屯門青山公路青山灣段168號翠濤居1座，早上11時許，一名男子報案指懷疑家傭將尿加入食物，將「加料」食物交給妻子食用，警方經調查後拘捕家傭。"},{"pid":"7f430ddd0c38493a822ad96babd7f87fe5d00044","tid":678417,"uid":34495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"又係賓賓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360f7930a810a2c90334104c16fc2ae7d4ada883","tid":678417,"uid":120715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f430ddd0c38493a822ad96babd7f87fe5d00044","tid":678417,"uid":34495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"又係賓賓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"鄉下地道風味<br />\n香港人唔識野"},{"pid":"ecb93dfc0e844b6c7b43b9d631160662fad20bdd","tid":678417,"uid":157362,"like":58,"dislike":7,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"960ba6b31bf708421ef09204fc3bad142c8101a8","tid":678417,"uid":34949,"like":79,"dislike":29,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"reply